and we're streaming live.

59:51.460 --> 59:55.085
Episode 28
of my Mindful Meditations.

59:55.168 --> 59:58.085
I hope my words will soothe
and enlighten you,

59:58.168 --> 1:00:00.293
or at least allow you
to watch CNN

1:00:00.377 --> 1:00:01.752
