lush with wildflowers

1:00:15.794 --> 1:00:19.293
and overlooking a peaceful,
undisturbed valley.

1:00:20.460 --> 1:00:23.251
You're like Julie Andrews
singing "The Sound of Music"

1:00:23.335 --> 1:00:27.043
with her arms open wide
and never dreaming

1:00:27.126 --> 1:00:29.418
she'd soon be trafficked
by the Catholic Church

1:00:29.502 --> 1:00:32.126
into becoming an unpaid nanny
under a Nazi regime

1:00:32.210 --> 1:00:34.293
and ultimately marrying
an employer twice her age

1:00:34.377 --> 1:00:36.251
in a scenario that could
more rightly be termed

1:00:36.335 --> 1:00:39.919
hashtag EdelweissMeToo,
hashtag NoneOfMyFavoriteThings,

1:00:40.001 --> 1:00:43.585
and hashtag SoonYeVonTrapp.
(CLEARS THROAT)

1:00:48.210 --> 1:00:49.877
Let's return to our hillside.

1:00:51.210 --> 1:00:53.293
You're happy. You're at peace

1:00:53.377 --> 1:00:56.001
because you're not allowing
political trauma

1:00:56.085 --> 1:00:58.251
to poison your bliss.

1:00:59.001 --> 1:01:01.710
Take a deep, healing breath

1:01:01.794 --> 1:01:05.126
and imagine that you're not
even on Twitter or Facebook

1:01:05.210 --> 1:01:06.377
or Xanax.

1:01:09.210 --> 1:01:10.877
Are you starting to feel better?

1:01:12.043 --> 1:01:13.085
More centered?

1:01:14.085 --> 1:01:15.126
More sane?

1:01:16.210 --> 1:01:18.418
♪ (TRANQUIL MUSIC CONTINUES) ♪

1:01:20.126 --> 1:01:22.251
